{"tid":2219170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果踢爆： 藍絲西醫工會會長楊超發涉嫌干預選舉 並聲稱因為暴動 四圍都有炸彈所以無留意授權票預先印有佢個名","createTime":"2020-09-26T16:56:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T03:43:43.000Z","uid":22556,"like":39,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"54a515327adafab35ea090efd1ce1fbef0280c1d","tid":2219170,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T16:56:00.000Z","msg":"成立54年、一直是政府諮詢對象的西醫工會，被指涉選舉不公。消息指，該會去年11月選出4名新幹事，惟發予會員的授權票上預印了會長楊超發的名字，最終楊持有的授權票高達近7成；候選人名單又於選舉當日突然更改。落選醫生向工會投訴安排，涉事的楊超發卻不避嫌多番干預調查，甚至欲委任他職及「頒獎」以圖收買投訴人。西醫工會至今未有回應事件。<br />\n<br />\n不過，有關授權票預印了會長楊超發的姓名，令簽署授權書的會員，等同自動授權楊代為投票。此外，該次選舉原本只有4名候選人參選，惟選舉當日，候選名單突然改變，其中1名候選人退出，再新增兩名候選人，變成5人爭奪4個空缺。<br />\n<br />\n曾在會上提醒楊超發不應處理今次投訴，惟楊仍多次主動發言，聲稱不知授權票預先印上自己的姓名，並歸咎去年11月選舉時正發生「反送中」事件，故忽略了授權票的問題，「因為暴動，嗰時四圍都有炸彈，又堵路呀嗰啲」，更自稱是受害者，「俾人擺咗上枱，無端端印咗我個名上去」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200927/75DJMFBJ7VCBRJTNMAZC6BF74Q/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2Wf5uQzR8PpCRnG1qeqCyE2KiwMOa6VvRxhIikP5IWs2PsHLbIgPNPdKY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200927%2F75DJMFBJ7VCBRJTNMAZC6BF74Q%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2Wf5uQzR8PpCRnG1qeqCyE2KiwMOa6VvRxhIikP5IWs2PsHLbIgPNPdKY&d=31jm0GaxjznMjcF0xOQh0sg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=5190c961\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200927%2F75DJMFBJ7VCBRJTNMAZC6BF74Q%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2Wf5uQzR8PpCRnG1qeqCyE2KiwMOa6VvRxhIikP5IWs2PsHLbIgPNPdKY&h=060c87fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200927/75DJMFBJ7VCBRJTNMAZC6BF74Q/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_sourc